{"tid":2196552,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂- 氣炸‧酒梅‧錦滷雲吞 (睇片！)","createTime":"2020-09-10T04:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T06:05:33.000Z","uid":30742,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"55447bcb2d28bd38f5bc033bc6cd621b2d85d4ad","tid":2196552,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BKOReLWojz8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBKOReLWojz8&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=a32482e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BKOReLWojz8</a><br />\n<br />\n氣炸錦滷雲吞其實係我買氣炸鍋之前已經係個心度mark左要整！ <br />\n細細個去齋鋪先有得食 <br />\n都好多年無食過喇！<br />\n自己用油炸又好嘥油 <br />\n能夠少油氣炸而脆簡直係完美！ <br />\n呢個一定要試，而家出面無可能咁足料喇！  <br />\n<br />\nP.S: 錦滷雲吞唔係酒樓炸雲吞！兩樣野黎！  <br />\n<br />\n另外，上次烤雞片有人話我條片太長係因為中間雞既處理應該拆出黎 <br />\n所以呢次我將蝦膠同魷魚都拆左出黎 唔知會唔會好d，<br />\n你地記得比意見呀！ 咁我下次可以再做好d！  <br />\n<br />\n簡易自製蝦膠教學 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3Axwqg2MV48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3Axwqg2MV48&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=669e5636\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3Axwqg2MV48</a>  <br />\n<br />\n魷魚處理教學 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/24svGUFlRvc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F24svGUFlRvc&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=4ff0531d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/24svGUFlRvc</a><br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜（呢次有埋gif！！！）<br />\n<a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2020/09/air-fryer-fried-wonton-with-wine-plum.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F09%2Fair-fryer-fried-wonton-with-wine-plum.html&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=33f3c88c\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2020/09/air-fryer-fried-wonton-with-wine-plum.html</a>  <br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=1a83afa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a> Instagram:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=994455de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a>  <br />\nBlog:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=6ffbe0e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"bf1874125c9473d025b2bfa581f037a498a3b58b","tid":2196552,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:09:13.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef86723a62720d67e6fb6d058bed13ab321779d","tid":2196552,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"氣炸師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0472dee8a2407a8988f624f4d9e00c465af5467","tid":2196552,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:12:00.000Z","msg":"錦滷雲吞和炸雲吞有咩分別？英文都係叫 Fried Wonton <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cd279626bc74cc784b1e562b415c311bd14cb1","tid":2196552,"uid":30742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d0472dee8a2407a8988f624f4d9e00c465af5467","tid":2196552,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:12:00.000Z","msg":"錦滷雲吞和炸雲吞有咩分別？英文都係叫 Fried Wonton <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />